climb into a drawer, 'cause
that's what marriage is like.

253
00:13:12,548 --> 00:13:14,032
Can I get an amen?

254
00:13:16,557 --> 00:13:18,581
- Is everything all right at home, Stuart?
- No.

255
00:13:27,576 --> 00:13:28,832
