don't worry about the show.

268
00:14:10,775 --> 00:14:12,173
Uh, we'd feel bad.

269
00:14:12,947 --> 00:14:14,211
What does that mean?

270
00:14:14,228 --> 00:14:16,232
No. We just mean, uh,
you're off the hook.

271
00:14:16,245 --> 00:14:17,563
You don't have to do it.

272
00:14:17,837 --> 00:14:20,410
