Well, guess what?

273
00:14:20,427 --> 00:14:25,140
I know I don't have to do it.
I do it because I am good at it.

274
00:14:25,198 --> 00:14:26,973
Look, I don't need your pity.

275
00:14:27,005 --> 00:14:31,073
