as it's brought me.

291
00:16:03,418 --> 00:16:04,800
Grandma, um...

292
00:16:06,848 --> 00:16:07,680
Wow.

293
00:16:08,225 --> 00:16:12,313
Well, take it out, honey.
I want to show you how to use it.

294
00:16:13,865 --> 00:16:16,243
Okay, no, no!
Don't take it out.

295
00:16:16,575 --> 00:16:19,183
Lily, that's not your grandma's gift.
It's mine.

296
00:16:19,206 --> 00:16:23,370
I panicked, and I switched the cards
because I was embarrassed.

297
00:16:23,407 --> 00:16:24,931
Well, what is it?

298
00:16:34,945 --> 00:16:39,133
It's just like the one Miranda gave
to Charlotte on Sex and the City.

299
00:16:39,178 --> 00:16:42,903
Oh, I love that show.
I always watch it on TBS.

300
00:16:43,016 --> 00:16:45,533
Oh, you would.
You're such a Samantha!

301
00:16:45,547 --> 00:16:48,041
Oh, I'm a Carrie!
You're a Samantha!

302
00:16:49,365 --> 00:16:52,471
And then the night became
a whole new kind of uncomfortable.

303
00:16:53,775 --> 00:16:56,283
