I may be done eating.

307
00:17:08,398 --> 00:17:09,450
Me, too.

308
00:17:09,647 --> 00:17:11,533
I mean, like, forever.

309
00:17:12,037 --> 00:17:13,083
Me, too.

310
00:17:13,578 --> 00:17:14,910
I miss my wife.

311
00:17:16,675 --> 00:17:20,201
Hey, let's go around the table
and say what our favorite part was.

312
00:17:20,305 --> 00:17:22,613
Mine was that thing with the typewriter.

313
00:17:22,995 --> 00:17:25,942
I mean, she made some
spelling mistakes, but still.

314
00:17:26,878 --> 00:17:29,513
Ooh, and you guys were all,
"Barney, put out the cigar!

315
00:17:29,528 --> 00:17:33,031
