to force an evacuation of the hotel,

323
00:17:52,128 --> 00:17:54,160
but definitely big enough
to get us kicked out,

324
00:17:54,177 --> 00:17:57,080
and bring Marshall's
bachelor party to an early end.

325
00:17:57,576 --> 00:17:58,581
Is that...?

326
00:18:00,375 --> 00:18:01,602
It is.

327
00:18:06,106 --> 00:18:07,342
Hey, guys.

328
00:18:10,027 --> 00:18:11,023
How was the fight?

329
00:18:14,728 --> 00:18:18,152
Hey, what are you guys doing here?
What happened to the bachelor party?

330
00:18:18,168 --> 00:18:20,590
We missed the fight, dinner was ruined,

331
00:18:20,616 --> 00:18:23,803
we spent half the night in the hospital,
and got kicked out of the hotel.

332
00:18:23,885 --> 00:18:26,353
- What do you think happened?
- Barney. Barney.

333
00:18:26,505 --> 00:18:28,480
Hey, I was just trying
to be a good best man.

334
00:18:29,048 --> 00:18:32,090
You know what a best man does, Barney?
He does what the groom wants.

335
00:18:32,178 --> 00:18:35,211
But all you ever think about is
what you want, what's best for you.

336
00:18:35,227 --> 00:18:36,131
Best man?

337
00:18:36,206 --> 00:18:38,432
I'm not even sure I'm inviting you
to the wedding at this point.

338
00:18:38,508 --> 00:18:39,620
You don't mean that.

339
00:18:39,637 --> 00:18:42,582
Why should I invite you?
You don't even want us to get married.

340
00:18:45,665 --> 00:18:46,983
That's not true.

341
00:18:47,318 --> 00:18:48,622
Lily, don't.

342
00:18:49,747 --> 00:18:50,592
What?

343
00:18:52,658 --> 00:18:53,782
I'm sorry, Barney.

344
00:18:54,137 --> 00:18:56,653
It happened last summer
when we were broken up.

345
00:18:58,807 --> 00:19:00,821
Hey, what are you guys talking about?

346
00:19:01,168 --> 00:19:02,950
- Lily.
- Ah, I got to go.

347
00:19:08,967 --> 00:19:10,472
Newark Airport, please.

348
00:19:18,707 --> 00:19:20,721
