of that happening,

363
00:19:51,007 --> 00:19:53,711
and I cannot keep stealing
chicks from him forever.

364
00:19:54,647 --> 00:19:57,702
Never, ever tell anyone I was here.
I will deny it tooth and nail.

365
00:19:57,718 --> 00:19:59,212
This trip never happened.

366
00:20:02,706 --> 00:20:04,663
Hey, if you had three hours to kill
before your flight, what would you do--

367
00:20:04,677 --> 00:20:06,802
Alcatraz or Fisherman's Wharf?

368
00:20:11,215 --> 00:20:12,503
You really did that?

369
00:20:16,507 --> 00:20:20,410
Marshall, I think Barney's
your best man.

370
00:20:21,207 --> 00:20:21,991
Yeah.

371
00:20:22,218 --> 00:20:23,242
Yes, he is.

372
00:20:23,247 --> 00:20:25,720
See, Lily?
This is why I didn't...

373
00:20:26,075 --> 00:20:27,470
- Really?
- Really.

374
00:20:28,675 --> 00:20:29,601
Real...

375
00:20:29,967 --> 00:20:32,620
In your face, loser!

376
00:20:33,776 --> 00:20:36,231
Take it easy, all right.
Ted's still my best man, too.

377
00:20:36,246 --> 00:20:38,043
You guys are co-best men.

378
00:20:38,045 --> 00:20:41,333
Right.
Yes, we're both best man.

379
00:20:42,677 --> 00:20:45,312
No, um, seriously.
You guys are co-best men.

380
00:20:45,406 --> 00:20:46,693
Of course.

